Detailed Description

cvmx_pip_stat_inb_octs_pknd#

PIP_STAT_INB_OCTS_PKNDX = Inbound octets received by PIP per pkind

Inbound stats collect all data sent to PIP from all packet interfaces. Its the raw counts of everything that comes into the block. The counts will reflect all error packets and packets dropped by the PKI RED engine. These counts are intended for system debug, but could convey useful information in production systems. The OCTS will include the bytes from timestamp fields in PTP_MODE.
